# Exo:

Data protection and recovery are fundamental aspects of data management. It's essential to have systems in place to ensure that data can be recovered in case of accidental deletion or corruption. 
The DevOps team has received a requirement for implementing such measures for one of the S3 buckets they are managing.

## Requirement:
The s3 bucket name is xfusion-s3-31475, enable versioning for this bucket.

Solution:
1- Log in to AWS dashboard with the providing crendentials **(For each Exercice)**.
  - URL: AWS console
  - Login
  - Password
2- Ensure the region at the top right is set to N. Virginia (us-east-1).
3- Search for S3 service and open it:
  a- Create S3 bucket
      Name: xfusion-s3-31475
      Keep the other informations as default
      Enable versioning
  b- save it and review the new bucket

